data.description: Welcome to the epitome of comforting home in Springville's MacDonald Farms neighborhood! Nestled within this picturesque community, we proudly present a stunning 4 bedroom, 3 and a half bathroom home that is sure to captivate your heart. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere that exudes warmth. The fenced-in back yard provides a private oasis where you can unwind and enjoy the beauty of nature. Additionally, the bonus room in the basement offers endless possibilities for entertainment or relaxation. And let's not forget the icing on the cake—the community pool, a perfect retreat for those hot summer days. Home has 2 new HVAC's and a new water heater. Don't miss your chance to experience the perfect blend of serenity and convenience in this remarkable home. Join us and embrace the lifestyle you've always dreamt of!
